assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Trinseo Plc, a materials solutions provider, manufactures and sells plastics and latex binders in the United States and internationally. It serves customers in a range of end-markets, including automotive, consumer electronics, appliances, medical devices, packaging, footwear, carpet, paper and board, and building and construction. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Berwyn, Pennsylvania.
